commit.message:
Modified Training Data

I have modified the training data a little bit.
removed youtube.py made picture delete after use
updates to driver.py rewrote gui.py works in one window and updates

Face Choice

The program will now select the largest face in the program's vision.
Finished the GUI. Added background, updated drivers.

Added Emotion-Music Constancy

If the dominant emotion does not change, then the function
will immediately return and leave the music as is.

Changed Metal to Heavy Metal

Apparently, "Metal" always plays Metallica, so we decided to
do Heavy Metal instead.

New Emotion Reading Scheme

We have developed a new mapping for the emotions onto the genres.
We also found an issue with the genre mapping from emotions, which
wasn't making the right transitions.

Camera works in OSX

Everything works
